Package scheduler

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Benchmark
    Class for Benchmarking multiple algorithms It also inherits from Service as to run in the background
    Benchmark.SolverData
    Local class to represent benchmark information about each Solver instance
    BenchmarkData
    Class that holds benchmark information for a single problem instance It is public as a benchmark is multiple problem instances for multiple algorithms.
    Controller
    Main Controller class for binding UI elements to methods & variables
    Main
    Main JavaFX application
    Problem
    Problem class contains all information about a scheduling problem instance
    Schedule
    A schedule is a special permutation schedule of operations It's stored as a HashMap of Points ( x : Job index, y : Machine index) A local list variable is added to store the scheduling
    Shade
    Workaround to packaging JavaFX 11 with the shade artifact This is redundant in development as accessing the Main class directly is possible
    Solver
    Abstract class to inherit from when creating a new Solver type It has helper functions to permute, combine, and parse schedules It inherits from Service to be able to solve the problem in the background
    Solver.JobData
    Local class to represent information about the current schedule list
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ShopType
    Enumeration for all shop types
